{
  "stem": "3331.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because we were very much interested in-- my father, even he was a Hasidic Jew, but he was very modern in his ways.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Like, for instance, he read a newspaper every day, where other ultra-Orthodox wouldn't read a newspaper.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And one in Israel-- and one in Palestine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- when I came back from the yeshiva, my dream was to go to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this was only-- as a matter of fact, in 1939, we couldn't go, because you needed a certificate from the English government to go in.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So there was a group, and we called it Aliyah Bet.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was the illegal aliyah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I app-- made an application with a friend, and we had to pay in $500 and to wait till a illegal ship will leave Constanta, Romania, to go to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I sent in, with my friend, and we waited, and we waited and waited.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "About three months before the war started, finally we got a letter what we should be ready, we should be packed, and we-- because any day we will get a notice to go.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the war started.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I was ready to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Also, I begged my brother in America.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I had a very large family in America.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because my father's six, seven-- seven sisters and brothers-- every one of them was in America with their children.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Except my father, because he was the only one very religious.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he always said that he wants his children should be brought up very Orthodox.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And all his brothers, all his sisters, were in America.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then, when I was 18, 19 years, I started to write letters and begged them to send me an affidavit to come to America.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And nobody sent me an affidavit.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
